               <p>MICHAEL AMBROSIA. I am an Italian. I was in <placeName id="t18271206-60-crimeloc298">King-street, St. Giles'</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18271206-60-crimeloc298" type="placeName" value="King-street, St. Giles'"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18271206-60-crimeloc298" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271206-60-off296 t18271206-60-crimeloc298"></join>, at half-past six o'clock in the evening of the 6th of November; I felt my pocket handkerchief go from my pocket - I turned round, and saw the prisoner run: I caught him with it - this is it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18271206-60-person446">
