            . I was in St. Giles', and saw the prisoner and another boy; the prosecutor came along, and the prisoner's companion spoke to him, as if he was asking the price of his images, while the prisoner took the handkerchief, and ran away. I told my father of it: the prosecutor caught the prisoner, and gave him to my father.</p>
